column5: This clip has almost attained European Pike status....or maybe Siamese Pike status....still don't get tired of watching though
interesting...   except we just watched someone die

no, apprently nobody died...which is miraculous...but this was all over the news a few weeks back, and it seems to be well documented that there were no fatalities.  Think about what would have happened if the pumps were busy....truly amazing nobody was killed

This clip was posted a week or so back. Beleive it or not the person driving the truck actually walked away unscathed.  Remarkable really, someone was for sure watching out for him that day thats for sure.
Here are the pics of the truck and trailer and shop after.

I'm going to take a wild guess that the driver was not wearing their seatbelt.  The way the cab is crushed, that's the only way they could've gotten out of the way enough.   The beginning of the credits say it all, "you lucky ba....."
